157 NPEffectiveGIMRprime::NPEffectiveGIMRprime(const bool FlagLeptonUniversal_in, const bool FlagQuarkUniversal_in)
158 : NPbase(), FlagLeptonUniversal(FlagLeptonUniversal_in), FlagQuarkUniversal(FlagQuarkUniversal_in)
159 {
160  if ((!FlagLeptonUniversal && !FlagQuarkUniversal)
161  || (!FlagLeptonUniversal && FlagQuarkUniversal)

163  throw std::runtime_error("Invalid arguments for NPEffectiveGIMRprime::NPEffectiveGIMRprime()");
164

454 
455 bool NPEffectiveGIMRprime::PostUpdate()
456 {
457  if (!NPbase::PostUpdate()) return (false);
458 
459  LambdaNP2 = Lambda_NP * Lambda_NP;
460  v2_over_LambdaNP2 = v() * v() / LambdaNP2;
461  if (FlagMwInput)
462  cW_tree = MwInput / Mz;
463  else
464  cW_tree = Mw_tree() / Mz;
465  cW2_tree = cW_tree * cW_tree;
466  sW2_tree = 1.0 - cW2_tree;
467  sW_tree = sqrt(sW2_tree);
468 
469  if (FlagRotateCHWCHB) {
470  CHW = sW2_tree * CHWHB_gaga - cW2_tree * CHWHB_gagaorth;
471  CHB = cW2_tree * CHWHB_gaga + sW2_tree * CHWHB_gagaorth;
472  } else {
473  CHWHB_gaga = sW2_tree * CHW + cW2_tree * CHB;
474  CHWHB_gagaorth = - cW2_tree * CHW + sW2_tree * CHB;
475  }
476 
477  delta_ZZ = (cW2_tree * CHW + sW2_tree * CHB ) * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
478  delta_AA = (sW2_tree * CHW + cW2_tree * CHB ) * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
479  delta_AZ = 2.0 * sW_tree * cW_tree * (CHW - CHB) * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
480  delta_h = CHbox * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
481 
482  return (true);
483 }

1163 bool NPEffectiveGIMRprime::CheckParameters(const std::map<std::string, double>& DPars)
1164 {
1165  if (FlagLeptonUniversal && FlagQuarkUniversal) {
1166  if (FlagMwInput) {
1167  if (DPars.find("MwInput") == DPars.end()) {
1168  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMRprime_LFU_QFU parameter MwInput" << std::endl;
1169  return false;
1170  }
1171  }
1172  if (FlagRotateCHWCHB) {
1173  for (int i = 0; i < NNPEffectiveGIMRprimeVars_LFU_QFU; i++) {
1174  if (DPars.find(NPEffectiveGIMRprimeVarsRot_LFU_QFU[i]) == DPars.end()) {
1175  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMRprime_LFU_QFU parameter "
1176  << NPEffectiveGIMRprimeVarsRot_LFU_QFU[i] << std::endl;
1177  return false;
1178  }
1179  }
1180  } else {
1181  for (int i = 0; i < NNPEffectiveGIMRprimeVars_LFU_QFU; i++) {
1182  if (DPars.find(NPEffectiveGIMRprimeVars_LFU_QFU[i]) == DPars.end()) {
1183  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMRprime_LFU_QFU parameter "
1184  << NPEffectiveGIMRprimeVars_LFU_QFU[i] << std::endl;
1185  return false;
1186  }
1187  }
1188  }
1189 
1190  //} else if (FlagLeptonUniversal && !FlagQuarkUniversal) {
1191  //} else if (!FlagLeptonUniversal && FlagQuarkUniversal) {
1192  } else if (!FlagLeptonUniversal && !FlagQuarkUniversal) {
1193  if (FlagMwInput) {
1194  if (DPars.find("MwInput") == DPars.end()) {
1195  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMRprime parameter MwInput" << std::endl;
1196  return false;
1197  }
1198  }
1199  if (FlagRotateCHWCHB) {
1200  for (int i = 0; i < NNPEffectiveGIMRprimeVars; i++) {
1201  if (DPars.find(NPEffectiveGIMRprimeVarsRot[i]) == DPars.end()) {
1202  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMRprime parameter"
1203  << NPEffectiveGIMRprimeVarsRot[i] << std::endl;
1204  return false;
1205  }
1206  }
1207  } else {
1208  for (int i = 0; i < NNPEffectiveGIMRprimeVars; i++) {
1209  if (DPars.find(NPEffectiveGIMRprimeVars[i]) == DPars.end()) {
1210  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMRprime parameter"
1211  << NPEffectiveGIMRprimeVars[i] << std::endl;
1212  return false;
1213  }
1214  }
1215  }
1216 
1217  } else
1218  throw std::runtime_error("Error in NPEffectiveGIMRprime::CheckParameters()");
1219 
1220  return (NPbase::CheckParameters(DPars));
1221 }
1222 
1223 bool NPEffectiveGIMRprime::setFlag(const std::string name, const bool value)
1224 {
1225  bool res = false;
1226  if (name.compare("MwInput") == 0) {
1227  FlagMwInput = value;
1228  res = true;
1229  } else if (name.compare("QuadraticTerms") == 0) {
1230  FlagQuadraticTerms = value;
1231  if(value) setModelLinearized(false);
1232  res = true;
1233  } else if (name.compare("RotateCHWCHB") == 0) {
1234  FlagRotateCHWCHB = value;
1235  res = true;
1236  } else
1237  res = NPbase::setFlag(name, value);
1238 
1239  return (res);
1240 }

1245 double NPEffectiveGIMRprime::CHF1_diag(const Particle F) const
1246 {
1247  if (F.is("NEUTRINO_1") || F.is("ELECTRON"))
1248  return CHL1_11;

1458 double NPEffectiveGIMRprime::GammaW() const
1459 {
1460  double G0 = GF * pow(Mw(), 3.0) / 6.0 / sqrt(2.0) / M_PI;
1461  double GammaW_tree = (3.0 + 2.0 * Nc) * G0;
1462 
1463  if (FlagMwInput)
1464  throw std::runtime_error("Write codes in NPEffectiveGIMRprime::GammaW()!");
1465  else
1466  return (trueSM.GammaW()
1467  - 3.0 * GammaW_tree / 4.0 / (cW2_tree - sW2_tree)
1468  *( 2.0 * (1.0 + cW2_tree) / 3.0 * DeltaGF())
1469  + 2.0 * GammaW_tree / 3.0 * (CHL3_11 + CHQ3_11 + CHQ3_22) * v2_over_LambdaNP2);
1470 }

1481 
1482 double NPEffectiveGIMRprime::deltaGL_f(const Particle p) const
1483 {
1484  double I3p = p.getIsospin(), Qp = p.getCharge();
1485  double CHF1 = CHF1_diag(p);
1486  double CHF3 = CHF3_diag(p);
1487  double NPindirect;
1488  if (FlagMwInput) {
1489  NPindirect = -I3p / 4.0 * ( 2.0 * DeltaGF())
1490  + Qp * sW2_tree
1491  * ( 0.5 * DeltaGF());
1492  } else {
1493  NPindirect = -I3p / 4.0 * ( 2.0 * DeltaGF())
1494  - Qp * sW2_tree / 4.0 / (cW2_tree - sW2_tree)
1495  *( 2.0 * DeltaGF());
1496  }
1497  double NPdirect = -0.5 * (CHF1 - 2.0 * I3p * CHF3) * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
1498  return (NPindirect + NPdirect);
1499 }
1500 
1501 double NPEffectiveGIMRprime::deltaGR_f(const Particle p) const
1502 {
1503  double Qp = p.getCharge();
1504  double CHf = CHf_diag(p);
1505  double NPindirect;
1506  if (FlagMwInput) {
1507  NPindirect = Qp * sW2_tree
1508  * ( 0.5 * DeltaGF());
1509  } else {
1510  NPindirect = -Qp * sW2_tree / 4.0 / (cW2_tree - sW2_tree)
1511  *( 2.0 * DeltaGF());
1512  }
1513  double NPdirect = -0.5 * CHf*v2_over_LambdaNP2;
1514  return (NPindirect + NPdirect);
1515 }

1704 gslpp::complex NPEffectiveGIMRprime::f_triangle(const double tau) const
1705 {
1706  gslpp::complex tmp;
1707  if (tau >= 1.0) {
1708  tmp = asin(1.0 / sqrt(tau));
1709  return (tmp * tmp);
1710  } else {
1711  tmp = log((1.0 + sqrt(1.0 - tau)) / (1.0 - sqrt(1.0 - tau))) - M_PI * gslpp::complex::i();
1712  return (-0.25 * tmp * tmp);
1713  }
1714 }

1716 gslpp::complex NPEffectiveGIMRprime::AH_f(const double tau) const
1717 {
1718  return (2.0 * tau * (1.0 + (1.0 - tau) * f_triangle(tau)));
1719 }

1721 double NPEffectiveGIMRprime::muggH(const double sqrt_s) const
1722 {
1723  double m_t = mtpole;
1724  //doulbe m_t = quarks[TOP].getMass();
1725  //double m_b = quarks[BOTTOM].getMass();
1726 
1727  gslpp::complex dKappa_t = deltaG_hff(quarks[TOP]) / (-m_t / v());
1728  //gslpp::complex dKappa_b = deltaG_hff(quarks[BOTTOM]) / (-m_b / v());
1729 
1730  /* L_eff = G_eff_t_SM*hGG */
1731  gslpp::complex G_eff_t_SM = AlsMz / 16.0 / M_PI / v() * AH_f(4.0 * m_t * m_t / mHl / mHl);
1732 
1733  //double sigma_tt_SM = trueSM.computeSigmaggH_tt(sqrt_s);
1734  //double sigma_bb_SM = trueSM.computeSigmaggH_bb(sqrt_s);
1735  //double sigma_tb_SM = trueSM.computeSigmaggH_tb(sqrt_s);
1736  //gslpp::complex tmp = (2.0 * dKappa_t * sigma_tt_SM
1737  // + 2.0 * dKappa_b * sigma_bb_SM
1738  // + (dKappa_t + dKappa_b) * sigma_tb_SM)
1739  // / (sigma_tt_SM + sigma_bb_SM + sigma_tb_SM);
1740  gslpp::complex tmp = CHG / v() * v2_over_LambdaNP2 / G_eff_t_SM;
1741 
1742  double mu = (1.0 + 2.0 * ( dKappa_t.real() + tmp.real() ) );
1743 
1744  if (FlagQuadraticTerms) {
1745  //Add contributions that are quadratic in the effective coefficients
1746  gslpp::complex tmp2 = dKappa_t + tmp;
1747 
1748  mu += tmp2.abs2();
1749 
1750  }
1751 
1752  if (mu < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
1753 
1754  return mu;
1755 }
1756 
1757 double NPEffectiveGIMRprime::muVBF(const double sqrt_s) const
1758 {
1759  double mu = 1.0;
1760  if (sqrt_s == 1.96) {
1761  mu += +1.123 * (1. + eVBF2_ZuL ) * deltaGL_f(quarks[UP])
1762  -0.531 * (1. + eVBF2_ZuR ) * deltaGR_f(quarks[UP])
1763  -0.705 * (1. + eVBF2_ZdL ) * deltaGL_f(quarks[DOWN])
1764  +0.136 * (1. + eVBF2_ZdR ) * deltaGR_f(quarks[DOWN])
1765  +2.662 * (1. + eVBF2_Wud ) * deltaGL_Wff(quarks[UP],quarks[DOWN]).real()
1766  -1407.72 * (1. + eVBF2_HWud ) * deltaGL_Wffh(quarks[UP], quarks[DOWN]).real()
1767  +14928.1 * (1. + eVBF2_Hgg ) * deltaG_hgg()
1768  -12.451 * (1. + eVBF2_HAA ) * deltaG_hAA()
1769  -21.274 * (1. + eVBF2_HZA1 ) * deltaG1_hZA()

2403 double NPEffectiveGIMRprime::muVH(const double sqrt_s) const
